All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AdvancedSettingsFrame
A frame that provides advanced settings options for keyword generation.
Categories
Enum representing various categories and terms related to products.
CosineSimilarity
Provides methods for computing cosine similarity and related metrics.
DataAccess
Provides methods for reading from and writing to resource files.
DictionaryTab
A tab in the AdvancedSettingsFrame that displays and allows editing of the keyword dictionary.
Entry
Represents a single dictionary entry with a primary term and associated synonyms.
EntryList
Represents a list of Entry objects with additional utility methods.
FileUpload
Enum for handling different types of file uploads and processing.
FileUploadFrame
A frame that allows users to select a file to upload and configure upload parameters.
JPanelHelper
JPanelHelper is a utility class that extends JPanel and provides convenient methods for adding and managing components using a GridBagLayout.
JPanelHelper.ComponentType
Enum for component types used to configure layout constraints.
Keyword
Abstract class representing a keyword with associated metadata.
KeywordDictionary
 
KeywordGenerator
Generates a sorted list of keywords based on relevance to a given input keyword or attribute set.
KeywordListPanel
A panel that displays a list of generated keywords and their associated data.
KeywordMatch
Represents a keyword that is matched against another keyword, with additional properties for orders, CVR (conversion rate), and score.
ListInfoTab
A tab in AdvancedSettings that displays the generated keyword list from KeywordListPanel.
Main
Entry point for the application, sets up the main application window
MainPanel
MainPanel is a singleton class that represents the main panel of the application GUI.
PanelTemplate
A template class for creating new panel types.
Product
Represents a product with a description and additional attributes.
ProductListTab
 
ProductSelectPanel
ProductSelectPanel is a panel that allows users to select product characteristics and generate keywords based on their selections.
SearchTerm
Represents a search term that a user has entered, used for searching on Amazon.
SettingsPanel
A panel for adjusting parameters related to keyword generation.
Tokenizer
Provides methods for tokenizing and processing keywords using Stanford CoreNLP.
TokenSearchTab
A tab in the AdvancedSettingsFrame that allows the user to search for tokens and displays products and search terms that contain the specified token.
UnclassifiedTokensTab
A tab in the AdvancedSettingsFrame that displays unclassified tokens and allows users to categorize them.
